5. Stakeholder Interests Documentation - Document stakeholder interests and influence
Stakeholder Interests and Influence 
Stakeholder	Interests	Influence Level
Employees	Easy reporting, quick resolution, transparency	Medium
Security Analysts	Efficient triage, clear workflows, reduced manual work	High

SOC Team	Real-time monitoring, coordinated response, comprehensive reporting	High
IT Administrators	System reliability, security, ease of maintenance	Medium
Management	Risk reduction, compliance, cost-effectiveness	High
Legal & Compliance	Adherence to regulations, proper documentation	Medium
